outputs.output_descr: The Purpose and Objectives of the Project are "Enhanced engagement in the multilevel aid coordination structure, enhanced analysis and strengthening access" through "enhanced research and monitoring and evaluation services to the PA, donors and UN" and "Enhancement of UNSCO's relationships with its Israeli interlocutors and improve support to the Humanitarian Coordinator on access issues".

project_descr: MAXIMIZING IMPACT - UNSCO	Maximising Impact 2010-2011, the Goal of the Project is Maximizing the impact of UNSCO in the oPt through ensuring a level of alignment between the UN, the LACS structure, the PA, local donor structures.
